<h2>What is a HoloBot?</h2>
<p>The HoloBots are a team from the <a href="http://techcrunch.com/event-info/disrupt-ny-2016/" target="_blank">2016 TechCrunch Disrupt New York Hackathon</a>. Using the <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-hololens/en-us" target="_blank">Microsoft HoloLens</a>, we brought <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Amazon-Echo-Bluetooth-Speaker-with-WiFi-Alexa/dp/B00X4WHP5E" target="_blank">Amazon's Alexa</a> in to the real world.</p>
