<h2>HoloAssist</h2>
<h3>The HoloBot Api Engine</h3>
<p>Join the club! HoloAssist powers the world's first Augmented Reality Personal Assistant, and now you can use it, too! You can interact with your <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook-com/" target="_blank">Outlook email</a>, detect emotions and tone with <a href="http://www.ibm.com/smarterplanet/us/en/ibmwatson/what-is-watson.html" target="_blank">IBM's Watson</a>, and get all your <a href="http://www.hmhco.com/" target="_blank">HMH learning and education resources</a> (with much more to come!).
</p>
<h3>The Current API
</h3>
<dl>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/mail" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/mail</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get your unread mail</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/tone?text=I%20%am%happy" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/tone?text={text}</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all available tones and they're scores of passed text (using IBM Watson)</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/tone/top?text=I%20am%20angry" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/tone/top?text={text}</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get the most likely tone passed text (using IBM Watson)</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/hmh/me" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/hmh/me</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all my info as a staff from HMH</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/hmh/mystudents" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/hmh/mystudents</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all my students from HMH</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/hmh/myroster" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/hmh/myroster</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all my schedule, term, and course info, as a staff, from HMH</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/hmh/mylearningcontent" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/hmh/mylearningcontent</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all learning content available to me from HMH</dd>
<dt><pre>GET</pre> <pre><a href="http://holoassist.club/hmh/mydocuments" target="_blank">http://holoassist.club/hmh/mydocuments</a></pre></dt>
<dd>Get all my documents from HMH</dd>
</dl>
